Package structure
========================================================

- R code (`/R`)
- Documentation (`/man`)
- Tests (`tests/`)
- Package metadata (`DESCRIPTION`)
- Namespace (`NAMESPACE`)

***

- Data (`data/`)
- Compiled code (`src/`)
- Installed files (`inst/`)
- Other components

