Description File
========================================================
```{r, eval = FALSE}
Package: greetings
Title: What the Package Does (one line, title case)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("First", "Last", email = "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: What the package does (one paragraph).
Depends: R (>= 3.4.3)
License: What license is it under?
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
```

